adept.common

Class DocumentRelationArgument.Filler

  • java.lang.Object
    • adept.common.DocumentRelationArgument.Filler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    DocumentRelationArgument

    public static final class DocumentRelationArgument.Filler
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A filler for a role in a document-level relation. Such role fillers may be of a limited number of different types, currently Entity, NumericValue, and TemporalValue. This class represents that uncertainty. The available types may expand in the future. Please see DocumentRelation for a full description of available relation classes. This class is locally immutable.
